    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702380/extras/22ec2382d01571adbc9115d76abd0cee.avif?t=1747317287\" width=616 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong> Have your own sea transport company <strong> </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transport cargo across the sea, buying and managing your ships and your team. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Coordinate cargo transportation and earn money </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Choose the best ships and complements at the dealership and make your harbor in the best way for you and your company. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hire and control your employees and have the best people at your side to help the company grow. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Manage your properties and expand your business. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Control your finances and invest your surplus money in the bank, or in difficult times try to get a loan from the bank manager. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Sign transport contracts and transport things massively, earning a lot of money </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Be a transportation entrepreneur, with control over everything in your business. Work, earn, invest and expand! </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1702380/extras/9c3710607de6b4cc84e04117fab19172.avif?t=1747317287\" width=616 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Success in sight, are you ready? </strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><strong><i> Deal closed!</i></strong></p>",
